question:
What is wrong with the following code?

```js
switch(value) {
  case 1:
    console.log('One');
  case 2:
    console.log('Two');
  default:
    console.log('Default case');
}
```

What is wrong with the following code?

```js
switch(5) {
  case '5':
    console.log('Match');
    break;
  default:
    console.log('No Match');
}
```

